title: "Nikolai Tretjakov - Natures Canvas"
date: 2024-12-30 12:00:00 -0000
author: Nikolai Tretjakov
quote: "From mountain peaks to valleys low,"
subject: Scandinavian Nature Poetry (Late 19th century)
permalink: /Scandinavian Nature Poetry (Late 19th century)/Nikolai Tretjakov/Nikolai Tretjakov - Natures Canvas
---

From mountain peaks to valleys low,
Nature’s canvas spreads so wide,
Painted with the sun’s warm glow,
Amidst the shadows, light does bide.

Let every heart be filled with grace,
As flowers bloom and rivers run,
In nature's arms, we find our place,
Where every moment is a sun.

- Nikolai Tretjakov
